'''卢希亚族''' （{{lang|en|Luhya}}，又称“Avaluhya”、“Abaluhya”、“Luyia”）<ref>{{cite book|last=Ember|first=Carol R.|coauthor=Melvin Ember|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=oGasFR3USxYC&lpg=PP1&ots=K-gU3xxehi&dq=Encyclopedia%20of%20Sex%20and%20Gender&pg=PA247#v=onepage&q&f=false|publisher=Springer|location=New York|isbn=9780306477706|title=Encyclopedia of Sex and Gender|year=2003|page=247|access-date=2012-02-08|archive-date=2014-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141215032650/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=oGasFR3USxYC&lpg=PP1&ots=K-gU3xxehi&dq=Encyclopedia%20of%20Sex%20and%20Gender&pg=PA247#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>是居住在[[肯尼亚|肯尼亚]]的[[班圖人|班圖人]]的一个[[族群|族群]]。<ref name="Jenkins">{{Cite web |url=http://orvillejenkins.com/profiles/luhya.html |title=The Luhya of Kenya |accessdate=2012-02-08 |archive-date=2016-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160121194245/http://orvillejenkins.com/profiles/luhya.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>其在[[乌干达|乌干达]]和[[坦桑尼亚|坦桑尼亚]]作为少数族群生活。<ref name="Jenkins"/>卢希亚族人口为610万人，占肯尼亚总人口（3850万）的16%。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://web.worldbank.org/WBSITE/EXTERNAL/DATASTATISTICS/0,,contentMDK:20394872~menuPK:1192714~pagePK:64133150~piPK:64133175~theSitePK:239419~isCURL:Y,00.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-02-08 |archive-date=2010-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100418131151/http://web.worldbank.org/WBSITE/EXTERNAL/DATASTATISTICS/0%2C%2CcontentMDK%3A20394872~menuPK%3A1192714~pagePK%3A64133150~piPK%3A64133175~theSitePK%3A239419~isCURL%3AY%2C00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

其使用的语言被称为卢希亚语（Luhya）。卢希亚族由18个部落（在部分情况下为19个，此时算上了Suba部落）。各部落都有自己的语言变体。“Luhya”或“Luyia”一词在部分语言变体中意为“家族”，“Abaluhya”意思即为“家族成员”。也有翻译作“在同一炉灶边的人”。

